import datetime
  
def calculateAge(birthDate):
    try:
        born = datetime.datetime.strptime(birthDate, '%Y/%m/%d')
    except ValueError:
        born = datetime.datetime.strptime(birthDate, '%d/%m/%Y')
        
    start = datetime.date(2019,12,31)
    age = start.year - born.year - ((start.month, start.day) < (born.month, born.day))
  
    return age

Model preparation¶

In [34]:
# removing total_traveltime since it's just the sum of layover_time and total_flighttime
passengersEU_clean = passengersEU_clean.drop(columns=['total_traveltime'])
In [35]:
def extract_luggage(luggage):
    numbers = ''.join([s for s in luggage if s.isdigit()])
    numbers = int(numbers)
    if "lbs" in luggage.lower():
        numbers /= 0.453592
    return numbers
In [36]:
passengersEU_clean['luggage'] = passengersEU_clean.luggage.apply(lambda x: extract_luggage(x))
In [37]:
passengersEU_clean['business_trip'] = passengersEU_clean.business_trip.apply(lambda x: 0 if x == 'no' else 1)
In [38]:
passengersEU_clean['traveled_with_family'] = passengersEU_clean.traveled_with_family.apply(lambda x: 0 if x == 'no' else 1)
In [39]:
passengersEU_clean['is_layover'] = passengersEU_clean.apply(lambda x: 1 if (x['departure_IATA_2']== x['shopped_at'] and x['flight_number_2']!='') else 0, axis=1)
In [40]:
passengersEU_clean['is_departure'] = passengersEU_clean.apply(lambda x: 1 if (x['departure_IATA_1']== x['shopped_at']) else 0, axis=1)
In [41]:
passenger_clean = passengersEU_clean.copy()

Indicator Variable für Geschlecht¶

In [42]:
#Erstellen der Indicator Variablen 0 und 1
passengersEU_clean['sex_indicator'] = passengersEU_clean.sex.replace(to_replace=['f', 'm'], value=[0, 1])
In [43]:
#Gruppierung und Count pro Kategorie für Männer und Frauen
passengersEU_f = passengersEU_clean.loc[passengersEU_clean['sex_indicator'] == 0]
count_f = passengersEU_f.groupby(["amount_spent_cat"])["sex_indicator"].count().reset_index(name="count_f")
passengersEU_m = passengersEU_clean.loc[passengersEU_clean['sex_indicator'] == 1]
count_m = passengersEU_m.groupby(["amount_spent_cat"])["sex_indicator"].count().reset_index(name="count_m")
passenger_sex = pd.concat([count_f, count_m['count_m']], axis=1, sort=False)
